0:19:43.110,0:19:46.052
Peace to Your Majesty.
Peace to Noble Lady Sourire.

0:19:46.240,0:19:47.800
You're already well-informed.

0:19:48.276,0:19:51.300
The Palace of Pearl Jade is honored
